1330
01:49:32,899 --> 01:49:34,476
Yes, my conscience.

1331
01:49:36,870 --> 01:49:38,817
He did us great good.

1332
01:49:41,133 --> 01:49:44,101
Do we all holy rites.

1333
01:49:44,754 --> 01:49:47,781
Let there be sung
non nobisandte deum.

1334
01:49:48,346 --> 01:49:51,403
The dead with charity
enclosed in clay.

1335
01:49:52,259 --> 01:49:54,029
And then to Calais...

1336
