health to you all.

1384
01:54:58,182 --> 01:55:03,814
Right joyous are we to behold your
face, most worthy brother England.

1385
01:55:03,914 --> 01:55:05,123
Fairly met.

1386
01:55:06,762 --> 01:55:10,656
So are you,
princes English, every one.

1387
01:55:19,407 --> 01:55:23,367
My duty to you both,
on equal love,

1388
01:55:23,825 --> 01:55:26,213
great kings of France...

1389
01:55:26,321 --> 01:55:27,499
and England.

1390
01:55:31,697 --> 01:55:35,758
Since that my office
hath so far prevailed,

1391
01:55:35,858 --> 01:55:39,758
that face to face and royal
eye to eye you have congreeted...

1392
01:55:39,858 --> 01:55:44,015
let it not disgrace me if I
demand before this royal view...

1393
01:55:44,115 --> 01:55:47,055
why that the naked,
poor and mangled peace...

1394
01:55:47,155 --> 01:55:50,351
should not in this best
garden of the world,

1395
01:55:50,451 --> 01:55:54,824
our fertile France,
put up her lovely visage?

1396
01:55:55,922 --> 01:55:56,922
Alas,

1397
01:55:57,810 --> 01:56:00,911
she hath from France
too long been chased,

1398
01:56:01,011 --> 01:56:04,488
and all her husbandry
doth lie on heaps,

1399
01:56:04,722 --> 01:56:08,332
corrupting in
its own fertility.

1400
01:56:09,170 --> 01:56:12,847
And as our vineyards,
fallows, meads and hedges,

1401
01:56:12,947 --> 01:56:15,855
defective in their natures,
grow to wildness,

1402
01:56:15,955 --> 01:56:20,912
even so our houses and ourselves,
our children have lost...

1403
01:56:21,012 --> 01:56:23,152
or do not learn
for want of time...

1404
01:56:23,252 --> 01:56:25,904
those sciences which
should become our country,

1405
01:56:26,004 --> 01:56:30,576
but grow like savages,
as soldiers will...

1406
01:56:30,676 --> 01:56:33,584
that nothing do
but meditate on blood...

1407
01:56:33,684 --> 01:56:38,384
to swearing and stern looks,
diffused attire,

1408
01:56:38,484 --> 01:56:41,711
and everything that seems...

1409
01:56:42,260 --> 01:56:44,016
unnatural.

1410
01:56:45,748 --> 01:56:48,881
And my speech entreats
that I may know...

1411
01:56:48,981 --> 01:56:51,121
the let why gentle peace...

1412
01:56:51,221 --> 01:56:53,905
should not expel
these inconveniences...

1413
01:56:54,005 --> 01:56:59,305
and bless us with
her former qualities.

1414
01:57:01,301 --> 01:57:04,818
If, duke of Burgundy,
you would the peace...

1415
01:57:04,918 --> 01:57:08,145
whose want gives growth to the
imperfections which you have cited,

1416
01:57:08,245 --> 01:57:10,194
then you must buy
that peace...

1417
01:57:10,294 --> 01:57:14,770
with full accord
to all our just demands.

1418
01:57:14,870 --> 01:57:19,506
I have but with
a cursorary eye...

1419
01:57:19,606 --> 01:57:22,322
o'erglanced the articles.

1420
01:57:22,422 --> 01:57:25,681
Pleaseth your grace to appoint
some of your council...

1421
01:57:25,781 --> 01:57:28,305
to sit with us once more...

1422
01:57:28,405 --> 01:57:31,122
we will suddenly pass...

1423
01:57:31,222 --> 01:57:34,514
our accept
and peremptory answer.

1424
01:57:34,965 --> 01:57:36,175
Brother, we shall.

1425
01:57:38,742 --> 01:57:41,683
Yet leave
our cousin Katherine...

1426
01:57:41,783 --> 01:57:43,058
here with us.

1427
01:57:45,749 --> 01:57:49,107
She is our capital demand...

1428
01:57:49,207 --> 01:57:52,750
comprised within
the fore-rank of our articles.

1429
01:57:58,134 --> 01:57:59,563
She hath good leave.

1430
01:58:17,240 --> 01:58:19,669
Fair Katherine,
and most fair,

1431
01:58:19,769 --> 01:58:21,813
will you vouchsafe
to teach a soldier...

1432
01:58:21,913 --> 01:58:24,213
terms such as will enter
at a lady's ear...

1433
01:58:24,313 --> 01:58:28,140
and plead his love suit
to her gentle heart?

1434
01:58:28,695 --> 01:58:31,732
Your majesty
shall mock at me.

1435
01:58:31,832 --> 01:58:34,933
I cannot speak your England.

1436
01:58:35,033 --> 01:58:36,341
Oh.

1437
01:58:39,224 --> 01:58:42,580
Fair Katherine, if you will love me
soundly with your French heart,

1438
01:58:42,680 --> 01:58:46,165
glad to hear you confess it
brokenly with your English

1439
